      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single static compression-bending configuration per ASTM F1717. Dynamic or torsional loading conditions not evaluated in this validation activity. Achieved level 2 (single condition) falls below required level 3; this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the medium decision consequence and the conservative nature of static compression-bending as a worst-case proxy."
