    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team-fda-osel",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for a medium model risk, medium decision consequence COU. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted because static compression-bending per ASTM F1717 is the regulatory standard test and represents a conservative loading envelope for this device class. Uncertainty quantification across material and geometric input distributions confirms that model predictions remain within acceptance bounds across the sampled input space. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a medium-assurance regulatory submission claim.",
